  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-894"><p>It&#8217;s funny you mention the &#8220;intuition.&#8221; My impression is that it was the first time shaving companies managed to pull one over on the ladies. But I&#8217;m no women&#8217;s shaving historian.</p>

<p>There&#8217;s &#8220;this funny article&#8221;:http://www.slate.com/id/2085175/ about Jewel selling her song of the same name for their commercial (and the song is about not selling out!).</p>

<p>About the cream: I guess we&#8217;re better off than you cause we don&#8217;t go through it that quickly, having a lot less surface area to cover.</p>

<p>It&#8217;s all the same though, any money spent just shaving hairs off your body kinda sucks.</p></div>
